<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ nǐ ér nǚ de mìng yùn zài nǐ shǒu lǐ, yuàn nǐ de zhēn lǐ bèi gāo jǔ.
 yuàn nǐ zài zhōng guó yǒu lì zú zhī de, wǒ men pò qiè de hū qiú nǐ.
 rú guǒ wǒ men dé zuì le nǐ, rú guǒ wǒ men yuǎn lí le nǐ,
 zhòng jiào huì yī tóng guì xià, xiàng nǐ rèn zuì. nǐ shì xìn shí de,
 nǐ yǐ lián mǐn wèi huái, kàn gù nǐ de shēn tǐ. nǐ yǐ lián mǐn wèi huái,
 bǎo shǒu nǐ de ér nǚ. bǎo shǒu nǐ de ér nǚ.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ nǐ ér nǚ de mìng yùn zài nǐ shǒu lǐ 迦南671</title>
